-- Metinvest Abandons Discussions to Purchase Severstal's Lucchini, MF Says
-- Armorel Kenna
-- 2010-04-23T06:53:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/metinvest-abandons-discussions-to-purchase-severstal-s-lucchini-mf-says.html

          
          
             Ukraine’s Metinvest abandoned talks
to buy Severstal OAO’s Italian unit Lucchini SpA, daily MF
reported, without saying where it got the information.  
 Severstal is no longer in a hurry to sell Lucchini,
according to the Italian newspaper. Tata Steel Ltd and
ArcelorMittal are also no longer interested in the Italian steel
company, MF reported.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Armorel Kenna in Milan at 
 akenna@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        